query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS performance_baselines (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  endpoint_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL UNIQUE,
  endpoint_path VARCHAR(500) NOT NULL,
  method ENUM('GET', 'POST', 'PUT', 'DELETE', 'PATCH') NOT NULL,
  avg_response_time INT NOT NULL,
  p50_response_time INT NOT NULL,
  p95_response_time INT NOT NULL,
  p99_response_time INT NOT NULL,
  min_response_time INT NOT NULL,
  max_response_time INT NOT NULL,
  warning_threshold INT NOT NULL,
  critical_threshold INT NOT NULL,
  sample_size INT NOT NULL DEFAULT 100,
  last_updated TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
)
